rows.name: Are you the one who sent the SOS?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0002

Super dangerous inside![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0008
rows.name:
But that doesn't stop New LA from needing
a secure source of flemtide, now does it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0010

Who cares about your job? You abandoned
your own family in there![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0011
rows.name: I left BECAUSE he's family. I finished my part of the job, see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0012
rows.name:
Cole Family Rule Number Four:
When the job's done, go home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0013

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0014
rows.name:
Well, that's why we called you, right?
I'll let you take it from here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0015
rows.name: I'll head back to New LA. Good luck![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0016
rows.name: Hey! What the hell is wrong with you? Get back here![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085302_MSG0018
rows.name:
I know, Irina, but there's no time to worry
about that now. We still have a mission to do.[ST:wait ]
